The Ijebu Nation has congratulated the All Progressives Congress national leader, Asiwaju Bola Tinubu, on his emergence as the presidential candidate of the APC in the 2023 general election. The congratulatory message, which was titled, ‘Hearty congratulations from Ijebu Nation’, was published in the 2022 Ojude-Oba magazine. The message read, “Your emergence as All Progressives Congress candidate for the 2023 presidential election was not by accident. “Yes, the joy of victory is reverberating all over the country. It is our conviction that your hard work, patriotism, goodwill, network, political sagacity and creativity, and other immutable attributes played a key role. The best is yet to come as we pray you become the next president and Commander-in-Chief of our dear country in 2023, God willing. “Keep up the ideals you stand for, Asiwaju Bola Ahmed Tinubu. “The Almighty God shall sanctify you and grant you the wherewithal to excel and take our country to the Promised Land (Amen). “Best wishes from Ijebu Nation.” A photograph of the magazine was posted by a Twitter user with the handle @SulaiOdus. 